{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_06_01",
  "title": "fran 1話 嘘、嘘でしょ……！？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさかラスベガスでもmihoさん達とケンカするとは\nfranさんはどこまで行ったんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe she’s fighting with miho-san even in Las Vegas…\nWhere has fran-san gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2766.6662852000004,
          "startTime": 7.5999996185
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.000000000001,
          "startTime": 9.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、いたいた。franさん！\nすぐに見つかって良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ there you are. Fran-san!\nI'm glad I found you so quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2666671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "人を迷子みたいに言わないで下さい。街の治安も\nいいですし、私一人でブラついても問題ないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t talk about me like I’m a lost child. This city has a good\npublic safety ‚ and there’s no problem with me wandering around alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.233333842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても腹が立つわ……。負け犬根性だのチキン\nだの。こっちは現実的な意見を言っただけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s so frustrating… Being called things like “loser mentality” and\n“chicken”. I was just giving my realistic opinion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.333333842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（franさん、大分怒ってるみたいだ……。このまま）\n（ライブには出ない、なんて言われたらまずいぞ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Fran-san seems really angry… If this continues）\n（It’ll be bad if she says she won’t do the live show…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あー……そ、そういえば喉が渇きません？\n向こうにカフェがありますね。何か買ってきますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… S-say‚ aren’t you thirsty?\nThere’s a cafe over there. I’ll go buy something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6666671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あからさまなご機嫌取り、ありがとうございます\nでもやめときます。知らないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the obvious attempt to appease me.\nBut I'll pass. Don’t you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2281854153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカのカフェで売られてるのって、大体サイズが\n大きくてカロリーもとんでもないんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Drinks at American cafés are usually huge‚\nand the calories are insane.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.833333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1000005086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "スタイルの維持に気を遣ってるのに\nカロリー爆弾なんて飲めませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m careful about keeping in shape‚\nso I can’t drink something that’s a calorie bomb.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……こっちでは日本以上に口にするものに\n気を付けないといけないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So‚ in America‚ we have to be more careful\nabout what we eat than in Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4666671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。私はパリコレ経験者ですから\n海外には慣れてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. I’m a veteran of Paris Fashion Week‚\nso I’m used to being abroad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.2000005086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、お子様舌のkanaだったら\n気にせず飲んじゃうんでしょうけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if it were kana with her childish palate‚\nshe would drink it without a second thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "映えは狙えそうですし、「明日ライブで\n一杯動くんだからいいじゃん」とか言って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks good on social media‚ so she’d say “It's fine\nbecause I'm gonna move a lot at the live show tomorrow” .",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1000005086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "流れるように悪口が出てきますね……\nそういえば、この後のご予定は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You badmouth them so naturally…\nBy the way‚ what are your plans after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ホテルに戻ってあいつらの顔を見るのも嫌だし\n適当に観光でもしようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to go back to the hotel and see their faces‚\nso I was thinking of doing some sightseeing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7333236695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2666570028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、近くにいい場所があるみたいですよ\n{user}さんも行きます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there seems to be a good place nearby.\n{user}-san‚ do you want to go too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8666570028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、交通費は{user}さん持ちで\nそのために追いかけてきたんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ you’re paying for the transportation.\nThat’s why you followed me‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6333236695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.099995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "財布になりに来た訳じゃないんですけどね……\n分かりましたよ。心配なので一緒に行きます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not like I came here to be your wallet though…\nFine. I’ll go with you because I’m worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666625977,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11066.670227100005,
          "startTime": 129.8333328248
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9033.336893799999,
          "startTime": 127.7999994915
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.003735299998,
          "startTime": 125.766666333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.336893799989,
          "startTime": 123.6999994915
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.336893799989,
          "startTime": 123.6999994915
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.4499994915
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.4499994915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗～！　ここの噴水ショー、有名なんですよ！\nこれを無料で見られるなんて、凄くないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ so pretty~! The fountain show here is famous‚ right?\nIt’s amazing that we get to watch this for free‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.2666661581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、こんな規模のショーを定期的に\nしかも無料でやってるなんて。ラスベガスは凄いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ to have a show of this scale so regularly‚\nand for free too. Las Vegas is amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "これがラスベガスのブランディングなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is Las Vegas’s branding strategy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.7333328248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "カジノだったら、VIP一人一人が日本じゃ\n考えられないような額のお金を落としていきますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the casinos‚ each one of VIPs spend\nan amount of money that’s unimaginable in Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5465955362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "そういう人達が落とすお金を利用して\nこうした無料サービスを充実させてるって訳です",
      "translations": {
